# UI primitive mismatch frame

**Full frame:** [mismatch-inspection-frame.md](../skills/afenda-primitive-contract/reference/mismatch-inspection-frame.md) · **Perf:** [react-best-practices-bridge.md](../skills/afenda-primitive-contract/reference/react-best-practices-bridge.md)

**Skill:** [afenda-primitive-contract](../skills/afenda-primitive-contract/SKILL.md)

Physical path: `components-ui/`. Virtual MCP import: `@/components/ui/*`.

## Before edit or approval

1. If user asked **review/evaluate** → **E0 only**: run M1–M10 mismatch frame; report before patch.
2. Ask the four pre-flight questions (duplication, state source, class purpose, primitive vs recipe) + adapter state mirror check.
3. Run E1–E12 + M1–M10 + P1–P8; use mismatch finding format for every issue.

## Hard reject (do not approve)

```txt
two visual mechanisms for one state
mixed state sources
dead classes
hardcoded slot strings
consumer-overridable data-slot
recipe styling inside primitive
unexplained pseudo-element classes
animation not aligned with primitive state
className required to make default usable
```

